{"tid":2019451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要令黃碧雲輸初選 係咪應該向長輩推薦下民協何啟明？","createTime":"2020-05-16T09:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T14:35:15.000Z","uid":101392,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b6495fa99c87e315b62f5416c27c3f720b38ec53","tid":2019451,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T09:40:51.000Z","msg":"連登仔本身點都唔會投黃碧雲<br />\n問題係本身老一輩民主黨班fans<br />\n<br />\n家中長輩如果係民主黨fans <br />\n取態都應該係鍾意傳統溫和泛民<br />\n難D勸佢地投本土/激進泛民（岑子杰、張崑陽嗰堆）<br />\n勸佢地轉投毛孟靜、民協何啟明比較容易<br />\n但毛孟靜近年都傾向本土<br />\n可以考慮向佢地推薦民協何啟明？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kalvinhokaiming/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkalvinhokaiming%2F&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=9d120400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kalvinhokaiming/</a>"},{"pid":"ed89fcb5dc6986c01bf417f2b09cc4439723272a","tid":2019451,"uid":244240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T09:43:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51c8169ce55fb37700a6e4c991b7fb8d5adfb032","tid":2019451,"uid":86246,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T09:47:03.000Z","msg":"岑子杰同張崑陽幾時變左激進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岑係社民連底 張多數打國際線 有d近眾志"},{"pid":"73032e7a81a98d9bd17857062202c4a67f43b0b5","tid":2019451,"uid":101392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"51c8169ce55fb37700a6e4c991b7fb8d5adfb032","tid":2019451,"uid":86246,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T09:47:03.000Z","msg":"岑子杰同張崑陽幾時變左激進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岑係社民連底 張多數打國際線 有d近眾志"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T10:01:48.000Z","msg":"相對嘅姐<br />\n眾志、社民連比起民主黨公民黨民協<br />\n算係激進 <br />\n至少喺長輩心中係"},{"pid":"ba7c81d1c4b2e1a4d61ea90c2a7671c6ac3d08ff","tid":2019451,"uid":5378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T10:02:37.000Z","msg":"岑子杰邊